{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"viewBox","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/viewBox","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG Attribute reference home</a></p>\n\n<p><code>viewBox</code>&nbsp;속성은&nbsp;특수한 container element 에 fit 하기 위한&nbsp;주어진&nbsp;graphics stretch 의 set 을&nbsp;명시한다.</p>\n\n<p><code>viewBox&nbsp;</code>속성의 값은 whitespace and/or a&nbsp;comma 로 나뉘어진&nbsp;<code>min-x</code>, <code>min-y</code>, <code>width,</code>&nbsp;<code>height&nbsp;</code>4가지 number list 이다.&nbsp;이는&nbsp;주어진 element 에 의해 설정된 viewport 의 bounds 에 맵핑되어야 하는&nbsp;user space 내의 rectangle 을 명시하며,&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/preserveAspectRatio\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">preserveAspectRatio (en-US)</a></code> 속성과 관계가 있다.</p>\n\n<p>음수로 이루어진&nbsp;width 또는 height 는 허용되지 않으며 zero 값은 element rendering 이&nbsp;불가하다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"usage_context","title":"Usage context","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Categories</th>\n   <td>None</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Value</th>\n   <td><em>See above</em></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Animatable</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Normative document</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/coords.html#ViewBoxAttribute\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Example","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"elements","title":"Elements","isH3":false,"content":"<p>아래 element 들은 <code>viewBox</code>&nbsp;속성을 사용할 수 있다.</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/symbol\"><code>&lt;symbol&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/image\"><code>&lt;image&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/marker\"><code>&lt;marker&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/pattern\"><code>&lt;pattern&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/view\"><code>&lt;view&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Tutorial/Positions\" title=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en/SVG/Tutorial/Positions\">SVG Getting Started: Positions</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Usage context","id":"usage_context"},{"text":"Example","id":"example"},{"text":"Elements","id":"elements"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"« SVG Attribute reference home","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"viewBox","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"viewBox","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"viewBox","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"viewBox","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"viewBox","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"viewBox","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/svg/attribute/viewbox","github_url":"https://githu